Day 28: 子载波间隔\n• Day 29: 导频子载波\n• Day 30-31: 复习+实践\n\nWeek 10：信道估计与均衡\n• Day 32: 信道模型\n• Day 33: LS信道估计\n• Day 34: 信道平滑\n• Day 35: 均衡器设计\n\n---\n\n第四阶段：进阶主题（2周）\n\nWeek 11：MIMO与波束成形\n• Day 36: 空间复用\n• Day 37: 信道探测\n• Day 38: 波束成形\n• Day 39: MU-MIMO\n\nWeek 12：WiFi 7新特性\n• Day 40: 320MHz带宽\n• Day 41: 4096-QAM\n• Day 42: Multi-RU\n• Day 43-45: 总复习\n\n---\n\n学习建议\n1. 理论与实践结合\n2. 建立知识图谱\n3. 关注验证视角\n4. 记录问题\n5. 定期回顾\n\n---\n\n推荐资源\n• 802.11-2020 标准\n• 802.11ax/y/z 修正案\n• Wireless Communications - Andrea Goldsmith\n• MATLAB WLAN Toolbox 文档\"\n                }\n            }\n        )\n    }\n} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10\n\n$url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$docToken/blocks/$docToken\"\n\ntry {\n    $response = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $url -Method Patch -Headers $headers -Body $updateBody\n    Write-Host \"Document content updated successfully!\"\n    Write-Host \"Document URL: https://feishu.cn/docx/$docToken\"\n    $response | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 2\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"Error: $($_.ErrorDetails.Message)\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":92375,"output":1255,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93630,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774749068870,"responseId":"0e9d8968c9e3ea56d51cc488d30a414c"}}
